    <div class='content'>
      <p>
        Héctor Juan Pérez Martínez, known as Héctor Lavoe, was born on <b>September 30, 1946, in Ponce, Puerto Rico</b>. He grew up in a musical family, and from a young age, he showed an exceptional talent for singing. Lavoe attended the Juan Morel Campos Public School of Music, where he received formal training that laid the foundation for his future career.
      </p>
